Maintainer: Cactus <medved_cool@mail.ru>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9.0.0), libxml2-dev (>= 2.9.1), libgtk-3-dev (>= 3.14.5), libzip-dev (>= 0.11.2), pkg-config (>= 0.28), gettext (>= 0.19.3), libsqlite3-dev (>= 3.8.7.1)
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Homepage: https://github.com/Cactus64k/simple-fb2-reader
